Amber Heard has proven to not only be a liar but an abuser as well. Mera is a heroine that is imbued with intelligence, strength and honor. Shes also extremely beautiful! All of those characteristics are found in forensic psychologist Dr Shannon Curry. 

We appeal to WB/Discovery to recast Mera with an actual heroine, Dr Shannon Curry.
